      },
      {
        "text": "*Community Forum Post*\n\n**Subject**: “Video Feed Drops After 3–5 Minutes” \n\n**Username**: SkyCapturePro \n\n**Message**:\n\n“Mine did that too. Turned out the 2.4 GHz band in my area was super crowded. Switching the drone’s Wi-Fi to 5 GHz fixed all the dropouts!”",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/f579e64c0ffd1fd2f495781456a5c816-scenario1_c.png",
        "key": "undefined-cdf9bada-48d5-443f-8edb-b133acbf4dd2",
        "layout": "text-top-right"
      },
      {
        "text": "*Social Media Troubleshooting Thread*\n\n**Platform**: DroneAdventures \n\n**User**: @RotorRookie \n\n**Post**:\n\n“If your drone is drifting, do a full compass calibration. I found the real issue was magnetized screws inside the frame messing with my compass!”",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/f579e64c0ffd1fd2f495781456a5c816-scenario1_c.png",
        "key": "undefined-91f68b3a-8101-4f9c-861a-555ac85b7c47"
