      {
        "text": "*Instructional Video “Maximizing Drone Battery Life”*\n\n**Segment Title**: “Proper Charging & Storage” \n\n**Key Points**:\n\n- The drone's batteries degrade over time if stored fully depleted or fully charged.\n\n- Damaged or old batteries can cause unstable voltage supply mid-flight.",
